---
// FAQPreview.astro
---
<section class="relative bg-slate-950 text-white py-24 overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-800">

  <div class="absolute -top-32 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-orange-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">

    <div class="mb-14 reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">
        Common questions
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">
        Straight answers. No fluff.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">

      <details class="reveal group border border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/40 p-6 hover:border-slate-600 transition">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium flex justify-between items-center">
          Why not WordPress or Shopify?
          <span class="text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Templates and page builders introduce performance and tracking limits.
          We build clean code so your website becomes a real business asset.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="reveal group border border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/40 p-6 hover:border-slate-600 transition">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium flex justify-between items-center">
          Who owns the website?
          <span class="text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          You own domain, hosting and full source code.
          No lock-in. No dependency.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="reveal group border border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/40 p-6 hover:border-slate-600 transition">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium flex justify-between items-center">
          Do you guarantee performance?
          <span class="text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Yes. Core Web Vitals and Lighthouse targets are guaranteed.
          If not reached, partial refund + continued fixes until achieved.
        </p>
      </details>

    </div>

    <div class="reveal mt-10">
      <a href="/faq" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition underline">
        View full FAQ →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
